# Generated Scaladoc trees and landing page written by `./mill docs.writeToDocsPublic`.
# Astro copies `public/` verbatim into `dist/`, so these are regenerated on every build.
/public/api/

# Laminar playground Scala.js bundle written by `./mill krueger.webapp.writeToDocsSrc`.
# Lives under `src/` (not `public/`) so Vite can bundle its `monaco-editor`
# import against `docs/node_modules/monaco-editor/` during `astro build`.
# Regenerated on every run; never hand-edited.
/src/playground/generated/
